languages.text: "Странная энергия у этой штуковины. Она баюкает, слышите? Нет?.. Голоса уснули".
"This thing here has a weird energy to it. Like it's singing a lullaby. Can you hear it? You can't? Even my voices have fallen asleep."
languages.original_text: "Странная энергия у этой штуковины. Она баюкает, слышите? Нет?.. Голоса уснули".

traits.locale_text: "This thing here has a strange energy to it. It's lulling. Can you hear it? No? The voices have fallen asleep."

languages.text: “这玩意儿散发着古怪的能量，让人昏昏欲睡。你能听到吗？你听不到？就连那些窃窃私语的声音都睡着了。”
languages.original_text: "This thing here has a weird energy to it. Like it's singing a lullaby. Can you hear it? You can't? Even my voices have fallen asleep."

traits.locale_text: “这玩意儿散发着古怪的能量，让人昏昏欲睡。你能听到吗？你听不到？那些窃窃私语的声音都睡着了。”

languages.text: "Diesem Ding haftet eine merkwürdige Energie an. Sie lullt einen ein. Hört Ihr sie? Nein? Selbst meine Stimmen sind eingeschlafen."
languages.original_text: "This thing here has a weird energy to it. Like it's singing a lullaby. Can you hear it? You can't? Even my voices have fallen asleep."

traits.locale_text: "Diesem Ding haftet eine merkwürdige Energie an. Sie lullt einen ein. Hört Ihr sie? Nein? Die Stimmen sind eingeschlafen."

languages.text: «Esta cosa de aquí despide una energía extraña. Es como un arrullo. ¿No lo oís? ¿No? Hasta mis voces se han dormido».
languages.original_text: "This thing here has a weird energy to it. Like it's singing a lullaby. Can you hear it? You can't? Even my voices have fallen asleep."

traits.locale_text: «Esta cosa de aquí despide extrañas vibraciones. Es como un arrullo. ¿No lo oís? ¿No? Las voces se han dormido».

languages.text: « Il émane une énergie étrange de cette chose. Elle évoque une berceuse apaisante. Vous l'entendez ? Non ? Même mes voix se sont endormies. »
languages.original_text: "This thing here has a weird energy to it. Like it's singing a lullaby. Can you hear it? You can't? Even my voices have fallen asleep."

traits.locale_text: « Il émane une énergie étrange de cette chose. C'est apaisant. Vous l'entendez ? Non ? Les voix se sont endormies. »

languages.text: 「ここには不思議なエネルギーがあるわ。子守唄を歌っているよう…聞こえる？聞こえない？私の声さえ眠ってしまったわ」
languages.original_text: "This thing here has a weird energy to it. Like it's singing a lullaby. Can you hear it? You can't? Even my voices have fallen asleep."

languages.text: "Buradaki şeyin tuhaf bir enerjisi var. Kulağa ninni söylüyor gibi geliyor. Duyabiliyor musun? Duyamadın mı? Kafamdaki sesler bile uykuya daldı."
